## Ticket: Laptop Charger Failure

**Issue:**
User reported that their laptop charger stopped working. The power brick indicator light was off, and the laptop was no longer charging despite trying a different power outlet and checking the cable connection.

**Root Cause:**
Faulty laptop charger (power adapter failure).

**Resolution:**
- Verified the reported symptoms indicated a failed laptop charger.
- Coordinated with Shipping Management to dispatch a replacement laptop charger to **James**.
- Advised the user to use the replacement charger upon delivery and confirm normal charging functionality.

**Status:**
✅ Resolved – Replacement laptop charger shipped to the user.
